<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - FIT APP</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <style>
       
        .carousel-item {
            height: 600px; 
        }

        .carousel-caption h5, .carousel-caption p {
            color: #fff; 
        }

        .carousel-caption a {
            color: #f8f9fa; 
        }

        .carousel-caption button {
            background-color: #28a745; 
            border-color: #28a745; 
            color: #ffff; 
        }

            .carousel-caption button:hover {
                background-color: #218838; 
                border-color: #1e7e34; 
            }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: bold; 
        }

     
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-toggleable-sm navbar-light bg-white border-bottom box-shadow mb-3">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">FIT APP</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target=".navbar-collapse" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                        aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="navbar-collapse collapse d-sm-inline-flex justify-content-between">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav flex-grow-1">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Página Inicial</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Exercicios" asp-action="Index">Exercícios</a>
                        </li>
                        @if (User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
                        {
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Receitas" asp-action="Index">Receitas</a>
                            </li>
                        }
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="navbar-nav">
                        @if (User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
                        {
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <span class="nav-link text-dark">Olá, @User.Identity.Name!</span>
                            </li>

                            {
                                <li class="nav-item">
                                    <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Usuario" asp-action="Sair">Sair</a>
                                </li>
                            }
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Login">Login</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">Registro</a>
                            </li>
                        }
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" style="width: 90%; margin: auto;">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/lib/bootstrap/imagemCarrossel1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." style="height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Exercícios físicos e rotina</h5>
                    <p>
                        Descubra como integrar exercícios físicos em sua rotina diária para uma vida mais saudável.
                        <a class="nav-link text-danger" href="https://vivariun.com.br/como-inserir-exercicios-fisicos-na-rotina-agitada/" target="_blank">Saiba mais</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/lib/bootstrap/imagemCarrossel2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." style="height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Nutrição e Fitness</h5>
                    <p>
                        Aprenda sobre a importância da nutrição no seu regime de fitness.
                        <a class="nav-link text-danger" href="https://blog.sabin.com.br/autocuidado/guia-de-nutricao-esportiva-2/" target="_blank">Saiba mais</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/lib/bootstrap/imagemCarrossel3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." style="height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Mitos Comuns sobre Exercícios Físicos</h5>
                    <p>
                        Desvendando mitos comuns sobre exercícios físicos para uma prática mais informada e eficaz.
                        <a class="nav-link text-danger" href="https://abreucardiologia.com.br/mitos-e-verdades-sure-exercicios-fisicos/" target="_blank">Saiba mais</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>
    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
</body>
</html>
